{"tid":1456132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求各位係機場既手足唔好送頭","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:19.000Z","uid":264072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9aaafdcc29c41bb40a41b2a69e0be82925cf52","tid":1456132,"uid":264072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"依家既情況係困獸困 <br />\n係機場既手足大部分都冇預裝會有狗入黎<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">red]癱瘓機場目的都大致上達成[/red]</span>[/size=5]</strong><br />\n<br />\n跪求你地而家走到就走<br />\n可以試下過T2, 當然手足們要睇情況<br />\n<br />\nBe water, stay safe<br />\n<br />\n我睇到尋晚811咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係唔想今日大家有咩事<br />\n尋日前線有晒gear都咁慘烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日機場大部分都係和理非 博唔過啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉場又好 返屋企又好<br />\nPlease stay safe."},{"pid":"843c9f1c87d7a42b55255f334c91651edb9bbb47","tid":1456132,"uid":264072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"我知我P牌仔 冇咩資格出聲<br />\n但跪求手足唔好送頭 咁送頭法唔值啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5db4b6ad73e4179f4bf1ede59bd0ff95e85624b","tid":1456132,"uid":264072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfd495a209c223bc97507b7f1267bf075bd2d225","tid":1456132,"uid":264072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}